        "generateUrl": "https://service.msci.com/",
        "setup": "For MSCI APIs that use key-based auth, sign in to the [MSCI Customer Center](https://service.msci.com/) with your named-user or service-account credentials. If you already have an assigned API key, open the API Key section and click `Generate Secret` to create the one-time-visible secret. If you do not yet have access, go to the relevant API page in the [MSCI Developer Community](https://developer.msci.com/apis), click `Get Access`, wait for provisioning confirmation, then return to the Customer Center to generate the secret. Store both the API key and secret safely; the secret is shown only once.",
